## Usage Example
```bash
from gofannon.base import BaseTool  
  
class NewTool(BaseTool):  
    def __init__(self):  
        super().__init__()  
  
    @property  
    def definition(self):  
        return {  
            # Define your tool metadata and configuration  
        }  
  
    def fn(self, *args, **kwargs):  
        # Define your tool functionality  
        pass  
```

